content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 21 ยง 1245.3 - Car loading and unloading

State Regulations

The Port Authority shall not be responsible for rail car
demurrage, nor for delays in unloading inbound cars; nor for delays in
obtaining cars for outbound shipments, unless it has failed to exercise due
care and diligence. Notes
